{"tid":932161,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港公會][魔獸世界]外國私服 Destiny of Alliance - Warmane Icecrown (2)","createTime":"2018-12-07T13:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T17:53:11.000Z","uid":73938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4f956934199c31922c3267062c0e7d6bca1091bd","tid":932161,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/001013_7e06527c6a1fbdffc65741d7e07f0cc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F001013_7e06527c6a1fbdffc65741d7e07f0cc4.png&h=a95bd7df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Warmane Icecrown係一個外國嘅大型巫妖王版本私服，而個伺服器已經開達八年以上，唔需要擔心伺服器嘅穩定性不足夠。而巫妖王版本中入面嘅Bug已經修復好多，基本上成就過一萬係冇問題嘅，任務方面都好少話做唔到。伺服器人數限制為12K，但平均每日上線人數高於15K以上，因此如果超過12K嘅人就需要等排隊進入遊戲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因伺服器限制12K人數嘅關係而且伺服器位於歐洲，所以香港時間8點左右就會開始需要排隊</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/001344_ad7a0e498fb6844a04f96291bfc89dc2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F001344_ad7a0e498fb6844a04f96291bfc89dc2.png&h=9378c4e3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">伺服器介紹： <br />\n<br />\n伺服器名稱：Warmane<br />\n伺服器分流：Icecrown<br />\n收費：全免(如想免排就需要課一次金 - 最低要課90HKD - 就可以永久免排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n陣營：聯盟 <br />\n經驗倍數：7倍 (專業熟練/金幣為3倍)<br />\n外掛：伺服器嚴格監管外掛，一被檢測就會被Ban永久。 <br />\n任務：任務因跟伺服器關係所以會係英文，但我地discord提供嘅插件清楚顯示任務的所在地，唔識英文都唔需要驚。而且打任務名上youtube就有教學/再者可以問下在線嘅朋友仔<br />\n延遲：250Ms左右，不太影響遊戲體驗，如想打PVP請使用VPN降Ping</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/001344_ad7a0e498fb6844a04f96291bfc89dc2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F001344_ad7a0e498fb6844a04f96291bfc89dc2.png&h=9378c4e3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">介紹：<br />\n<br />\n我地係一班鍾意玩呢個版本嘅香港人組成嘅群組，自一年前開始組成，經過Wotlk香港私服嘅事件後，我地再次回到外國私服遊玩！我地平時使用嘅聊天軟件為Discord，公會平時上線人數為20-30人左右，希望黎到多啲人一齊撐起個公會，公會已經組緊第三團固定10人團隊，老手基本上都冇介入固定10人團，給予更多新人機會打團本。同時間我地都不時組織PVP活動，一齊每日殺部落、打戰場等等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">十分歡迎以前係香港私服嘅戰友一齊返返黎玩，冇分部落同聯盟，大家都係自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">-Discord群：</span><br />\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/5GCg2Sj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2F5GCg2Sj&d=KLjtiXc3fQ3DmHQ9vMEc97%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1d7a7cb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/5GCg2Sj</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-Discord下載：</span><br />\n  <a href=\"https://discordapp.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscordapp.com%2F&d=KLjtiXc3fQ3DmHQ9vMEc97%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=4f3b6379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discordapp.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-Warmane官網：</span><br />\n  <a href=\"https://www.warmane.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.warmane.com%2F&d=KLjtiXc3fQ3DmHQ9vMEc97%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=740cd610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.warmane.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-註冊帳號：</span><br />\n  <a href=\"https://www.warmane.com/account/create\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.warmane.com%2Faccount%2Fcreate&d=KLjtiXc3fQ3DmHQ9vMEc97%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1a6d9597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.warmane.com/account/create</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-遊戲下載：</span><br />\n  <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE%2Fview&d=KLjtiXc3fQ3DmHQ9vMEc97%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7f9b02fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE/view</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-註冊完/下載完仲差幾步就玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Step.1 下載登錄器<br />\n  <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU&d=KLjtiXc3fQ3DmHQ9vMEc97%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7df4d8a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU</a><br />\n  Step.2 放係遊戲主目錄開啟<br />\n  Step.3 開Game就可以玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如有問題歡迎入Discord咨詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-最近公會進度</span>：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">ICC - 10人主力團(12NM/12) (11HC/12) 拓荒HC巫妖王中<br />\nICC - 10人二團(12NM/12) (9HC/12) <br />\nICC - 10人三團(12NM/12) (9HC/12) <br />\nICC - 10人四團(12NM/12) (9HC/12) <br />\n<br />\nICC - 25人團隊 (12NM/12) (8HC/12) 最近ICC25人NM團隊拓荒已經完畢 恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yciZHpi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyciZHpi.png&h=42a3aa7b&s={SIZE}\" /></div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">黎緊我地公會會係下禮拜六15/12搞活動，活動分別為PVP競技以及跑步遊走大亂鬥。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">-PVP競技<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">將於(納格蘭-試煉競技場)進行三打三PVP競技<br />\n到時候將由官員裁判進行隨機分組<br />\n任何人都可以參加<br />\n詳情到時候會再進行詳細介紹<br />\n<br />\n名額根據到時參與人數再安排<br />\n獎品：10Coin + 10DKP</span><br />\n<br />\n-跑步遊走大亂鬥<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">到時候所有人均需要開一位矮人一級小號<br />\n於出生點集合以及入組<br />\n再徒腳跑步到洛克莫丹的洛克湖中間的小島<br />\n先到者勝出<br />\n詳情到時會再進行講解<br />\n<br />\n名額三名<br />\n獎品：10Coin + 10DKP </span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望大家踴躍參與公會活動，慶祝聖誕！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-!PVP活動限50級以上參加!-<br />\n<br />\n-!跑步遊戲沒有等級限制，任何人都可以參加!-<br />\n<br />\nCoin係遊戲交易貨幣 10Coin 價值100HKD ，可以獲得免排隊服務以及10個遊戲貨幣，拎黎換裝買坐騎都得</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"309cc767ebc58aff511d39fe94c09c41aca90922","tid":932161,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cec0a73f9271bc1570baa81e471aced9056eee","tid":932161,"uid":198929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T18:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc3b559d154498079965926fca68dc7099d5ab0","tid":932161,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39228d48b15a71f04f58efee698e33da8abe077f","tid":932161,"uid":198929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1219811b79377a718ddd4fed64dd2fe27a507f","tid":932161,"uid":58374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:18:49.000Z","msg":"正喎"},{"pid":"a0d206523babfab6df58dea2615adda8a16a6c59","tid":932161,"uid":96651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:48:52.000Z","msg":"好想玩"},{"pid":"1e00beffc88c02d7a669e66455c5c49d584197d1","tid":932161,"uid":198929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"推撚＂"},{"pid":"afd86c3b8776a03f5bc43feb992fae5b0968f13d","tid":932161,"uid":198929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e00beffc88c02d7a669e66455c5c49d584197d1","tid":932161,"uid":198929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"推撚＂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:26:13.000Z","msg":"*爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df510bfe14d30196d6aeb57433200e12c51395c2","tid":932161,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:20:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /